                +----------------+
                | Address Decode |
                +--------+-------+
                         |
          +--------------+--------------+
          |                             |
          v                             v

    Write Logic                  Read Logic

          |                             |
          +--------------+--------------+
                         |
                  Register Bank
                         |
                  Interrupt Logic
                         |
                      gpio_irq
